    "body": "Adds config for CQL(Cassandra Query Language) language server.\r\n\r\n- [cqlls](https://github.com/Akzestia/cqlls)\r\n\r\nFor the new config requirements, don't have 100 stars, but here are some things that u may consider:\r\n\r\n- 40k~ installs on CQL extension in zed(my beloved NSFW editor xD). [zed-cql](https://zed.dev/extensions/?query=cql)\r\n- 1.5k installs from [crates.io](https://crates.io/crates/cqlls) on the old one `cql_lsp`, and about 100 on the new one `cqlls` (related release: [cqlls v3.0.0](https://github.com/Akzestia/cqlls/releases/tag/v2.0.0))\r\n\r\nAlso not directly related to the language server itself but I guess worth mentioning:\r\n\r\n- CQL support for github (since github-linguist [v9.4.0](https://github.com/github-linguist/linguist/pull/7720))\r\n- Tree-sitter [grammar](https://github.com/Akzestia/tree-sitter-cql) for CQL\r\n\r\nSome language server demos ^_^: \r\n\r\nhttps://github.com/user-attachments/assets/d163e022-3933-416d-bb52-04a2e005756c\r\n\r\nhttps://github.com/user-attachments/assets/5c125ad7-31d5-4e6c-99cb-4c602c8773c8",
